Description: AI infrastructure scanner and profiler
 A purpose-built scanner for AI and machine learning infrastructure.
 It fingerprints 23 AI/ML service types (LLMs, vector databases, etc.)
 and includes a companion Python script for target classification
 and disclosure routing.
